59:19.990 --> 59:22.868
Anyway, I'm here, and I don't
plan on going just now.

59:25.070 --> 59:26.389
Let's do it.

59:32.790 --> 59:33.779
On "three."

59:33.990 --> 59:36.265
Wait, let me get into the tub.

59:36.710 --> 59:38.621
I'm just gonna give you the...

59:39.190 --> 59:41.306
On "three," huh? What do you say?

59:43.710 --> 59:44.825
One...

59:45.790 --> 59:47.701
