- Well, it's your ass.

59:57.270 --> 59:58.305
It's up to you.

59:59.590 --> 01:00:00.864
My ass, yeah.

01:00:01.270 --> 01:00:02.259
"Three."

01:00:02.590 --> 01:00:03.989
We go on "three"?

01:00:04.190 --> 01:00:06.499
"One, two" and then "three"!

01:00:09.910 --> 01:00:10.899
One...

01:00:11.230 --> 01:00:12.549
- Martin?
- What?

01:00:19.110 --> 01:00:20.179
I know.

01:00:21.310 --> 01:00:22.823
I mean it, man.

01:00:25.670 --> 01:00:26.944
I hear you.

01:00:29.550 --> 01:00:31.780
We're not gonna fucking die,
all right?

01:00:32.950 --> 01:00:34.065
On "three."

01:00:34.990 --> 01:00:36.184
One...

01:00:36.990 --> 01:00:37.979
...two...

01:00:38.390 --> 01:00:39.459
...three!

01:00:48.630 --> 01:00:50.109
I gotta go! I gotta go!

01:01:07.590 --> 01:01:10.741
