I'm here already.

01:04:52.910 --> 01:04:54.628
I should have known.

01:04:57.030 --> 01:04:58.429
Well, well.

01:04:59.070 --> 01:05:01.300
It's the master race!

01:05:02.350 --> 01:05:05.148
I hope you realize the trouble
you are in right now.

01:05:05.710 --> 01:05:09.100
As usual, you have everything
upside down and turned around...

01:05:09.310 --> 01:05:10.629
...and back to front.

01:05:10.830 --> 01:05:12.183
Gentlemen...

01:05:12.710 --> 01:05:15.065
