01:05:20.270 --> 01:05:21.259
Fingers off.

01:05:21.470 --> 01:05:22.698
Hand off!

01:05:23.790 --> 01:05:25.781
Let me look at that.

01:05:28.030 --> 01:05:31.705
That's some piece of hardware.
Where the fuck do you get that stuff?

01:05:31.910 --> 01:05:34.743
