...Rika, Vicki. How much
fucking authority do you need?

01:32:24.670 --> 01:32:26.103
You got a plan?

01:32:30.350 --> 01:32:32.864
If you drive around
the front of the house...

01:32:33.070 --> 01:32:35.106
...you wait for my signal...

01:32:35.790 --> 01:32:38.463
...and then just go in
and shoot those fuckers.

01:32:38.670 --> 01:32:39.659
They got Leo.

01:32:42.030 --> 01:32:43.258
Be careful.

01:32:51.710 --> 01:32:52.699
What's your signal?

01:32:54.070 --> 01:32:56.026
You'll know it when it happens.

01:32:58.670 --> 01:33:01.059
Somehow I think I will know.

01:33:32.390 --> 01:33:33.664
Payday.

01:33:46.910 --> 01:33:48.582
Feel like talking, Leo?

01:33:53.550 --> 01:33:54.665
It's the big one!

01:33:59.070 --> 01:34:00.105
All right. Cool it.

01:34:00.310 --> 01:34:02.619
- Watch him.
- Move me away from the windows!

01:34:34.670 --> 01:34:35.625
Watch the glass!

01:34:35.830 --> 01:34:36.865
- Come on!
- I'll go.

01:35:10.870 --> 01:35:13.065
Riggs, you crazy mother...

01:35:28.990 --> 01:35:30.742
Holy Christ!

01:35:34.710 --> 01:35:35.825
You all right?

01:35:36.070 --> 01:35:37.059
I'm okay.

01:35:37.270 --> 01:35:38.305
Thanks.

01:35:39.350 --> 01:35:41.420
- Was Adolf in there?
- He got away.

01:35:42.350 --> 01:35:44.227
- I'm gonna find him.
- What about Leo?

01:35:44.430 --> 01:35:45.499
What about Leo?

01:35:45.710 --> 01:35:47.587
You're on your own now, Leo.

01:35:47.790 --> 01:35:49.189
What do you mean?

01:35:49.390 --> 01:35:52.700
Take my car to the station
and wait for the federal marshal.

01:35:52.910 --> 01:35:55.060
It's been an experience knowing you.

01:35:59.230 --> 01:36:02.108
- I don't want a hug.
- Give the little fellow a hug.

01:36:02.350 --> 01:36:04.102
I had a lot of fun.

01:36:04.710 --> 01:36:06.348
You do your duty now.

01:36:06.550 --> 01:36:08.745
Don't worry.
I'll really get them now.

01:36:08.950 --> 01:36:11.259
- Listen! Wait!
- You know how to find him.

01:36:11.470 --> 01:36:13.461
Is it okay if I sound the siren?

01:36:15.910 --> 01:36:17.104
Loud as you want.

01:36:17.350 --> 01:36:18.339
Really?

01:36:18.550 --> 01:36:20.745
- Okay. Really?
- Bye, Leo.

01:36:25.310 --> 01:36:26.584
<i>Check it out.</i>

01:36:26.910 --> 01:36:30.266
<i>The Alba Varden is
a cargo ship, not a woman.</i>

01:36:30.470 --> 01:36:33.826
<i>The Port Authority said that
the Alba Varden arrived today...</i>

01:36:34.030 --> 01:36:36.783
<i>... and heads out tomorrow
to South Africa.</i>

01:36:38.790 --> 01:36:40.621
This is the 11 th dock.

01:36:40.830 --> 01:36:43.708
It must be here someplace.
I know I'm right.

01:36:48.750 --> 01:36:49.626
The ship.

01:36:49.830 --> 01:36:51.263
What did I tell you?

01:36:52.990 --> 01:36:55.629
That container there,
with three heavy hitters.

01:36:55.830 --> 01:36:56.899
Let's have a look.

01:36:58.670 --> 01:37:00.900
I'll take two of them out.
You take one.

01:37:02.550 --> 01:37:06.338
Better yet, you take two,
I'll take one. Pull over.

01:37:51.870 --> 01:37:52.939
I can't see shit.

01:37:53.150 --> 01:37:54.947
Me either. What is this shit?

01:37:55.150 --> 01:37:56.629
Got a light?

01:37:58.150 --> 01:38:00.186
It's gotta be Rudd's, whatever it is.

01:38:00.390 --> 01:38:02.506
I still can't see shit.

01:38:04.270 --> 01:38:07.467
- You got something?
- I don't know. It's a car.

01:38:12.390 --> 01:38:14.779
Holy shit. Fort Kno x!

01:38:17.910 --> 01:38:19.821
Hell, how much is it?

01:38:21.430 --> 01:38:22.863
Thousands.

01:38:24.350 --> 01:38:26.227
Fucking millions!

01:38:26.550 --> 01:38:29.144
Billions!
A fucking Donald Trump lotto!

01:38:38.910 --> 01:38:39.865
Look at this.

01:38:40.590 --> 01:38:42.785
These are thousand-dollar bills.

01:38:44.430 --> 01:38:48.423
With what I'm holding, I could put
all three of my kids through college.

01:38:49.710 --> 01:38:50.699
Take it.

01:38:57.990 --> 01:38:59.423
Fucking drug money.

01:38:59.630 --> 01:39:01.222
Do something good with it.

01:39:01.430 --> 01:39:04.024
Rudd won't need it where he's going.

01:39:16.070 --> 01:39:17.788
Load the container.

01:39:18.030 --> 01:39:21.545
Next time the sun hits their bodies,
they'll be in Cape Town.

01:39:25.430 --> 01:39:28.149
- This thing's moving.
- It sure as hell is.

01:39:28.390 --> 01:39:30.984
- What are we gonna do now?
- I don't know.

01:39:31.510 --> 01:39:32.909
Let's shoot our way out.

01:39:33.110 --> 01:39:35.021
Don't do that. I got a better idea.

01:40:27.390 --> 01:40:28.823
Our money.

01:40:31.710 --> 01:40:33.940
Just make sure they're dead.

01:40:44.270 --> 01:40:47.785
- You go first. I'm too old.
- No, you go first. I'll cover you.

01:41:02.470 --> 01:41:04.620
- How do we get out?
- I'm going this way.

01:41:04.830 --> 01:41:06.980
I'll go this way.
I'll check over here.

01:41:24.310 --> 01:41:25.345
Rog!

01:41:26.470 --> 01:41:27.539
Rog!

01:42:21.270 --> 01:42:22.339
Shit!

01:44:26.270 --> 01:44:27.988
Riggs, you okay?

01:44:44.070 --> 01:44:45.219
Drop it, asshole!

01:44:51.150 --> 01:44:53.710
Diplomatic immunity!

01:45:03.550 --> 01:45:06.018
It's just been revoked.

01:46:20.630 --> 01:46:23.508
You're breathing. You're alive.
You're not dead.

01:46:23.910 --> 01:46:25.343
No, don't die.

01:46:26.630 --> 01:46:29.190
You're not dead until I tell you.

01:46:29.390 --> 01:46:33.178
You got that, Riggs?
You're not dead until I tell you.

01:46:33.390 --> 01:46:34.948
You got that, Riggs?

01:46:35.150 --> 01:46:37.903
You're not dead until I tell you.

01:46:38.150 --> 01:46:40.106
Now breathe with me. Breathe.

01:46:40.310 --> 01:46:41.868
- Now, breathe.
- Hey, Rog.

01:46:46.830 --> 01:46:49.060
Rog, in my pocket.

01:46:56.510 --> 01:46:59.502
I want you to throw those things away.

01:46:59.710 --> 01:47:02.270
Those things will kill you. Really.

01:47:08.030 --> 01:47:09.861
You son of a bitch!

01:47:11.230 --> 01:47:12.583
I thought you were dying.

01:47:13.070 --> 01:47:16.142
I didn't die on your toilet,
I'm not dying in your arms.

01:47:16.350 --> 01:47:17.863
You son of a bitch.

01:47:22.710 --> 01:47:25.986
Are they all gone? The bad guys?
Did you get them?

01:47:26.350 --> 01:47:28.545
<i>They been de-kaffirnated.</i>

01:47:36.950 --> 01:47:39.589
Don't make me laugh! Oh, Jesus.

01:47:41.990 --> 01:47:44.060
Did anyone ever tell you...

01:47:46.150 --> 01:47:48.584
...you really are a beautiful man?

01:47:52.910 --> 01:47:54.741
Give us a kiss before they come.

01:47:56.790 --> 01:47:58.906
Where'd that bullet hit you anyway?

01:48:03.390 --> 01:48:04.903
Don't make me laugh!

